        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks FM for letter of 22 Feb [not found] on Lepidoptera. Will send it to Entomological Society to be read. FM’s earlier letters produced best discussions of the season.</p> 
<p>Thanks for seeds of <hi rend="italic">Viola</hi>.</p> 
            <p>He and Francis [Darwin] are at work on biology of seedling plants and wish to observe how the flowers penetrate the earth.</p> 
<p>The <hi rend="italic">Pontederia</hi> did not germinate, probably pressed too much [in post].</p> 
        </abstract>
